HEADWORD: Misword
<hw>Mis*word"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To word wrongly;
<as>as, to <ex>misword</ex> a message, or a sentence</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Misword</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Misword
<hw>Mis*word"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A word wrongly spoken; a cross
word.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Sylvester.</au>
<au>Breton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Misworship</ent>⟦br⟧
